			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2549585">
									

<p>Dr. Bright must disclose the full list of things he is not allowed to do at the Foundation to all new personel he meets for the first time. Dr. Bright must also inform his coworkers of his new restrictions by formal &quot;memo&quot; and provide the newly revised list accordingly.</p>
